AMAPPS 10 km Grid

Source: R/data_amapps_grid.R
amapps_grid.Rd

A raster object containing the Atlantic Marine Assessment Program for Protected Species (AMAPPS) 10 km grid. The AMAPPS grid has a cell size of 10 km x 10 km, with an oblique Mercator projection. Grid cell values represent grid cell IDs.

data("amapps_grid")

Format

A raster object:

class

RasterLayer

dimensions

328, 240, 78720 (nrow, ncol, ncell)

resolution

10000 m, 10000 m (x, y)

extent

-820443.2, 1579557, -1234728, 2045272 (xmin, xmax, ymin, ymax)

crs

+proj=omerc +lat_0=35 +lonc=-75 +alpha=40 +gamma=40 +k=0.9996 +x_0=0 +y_0=0 +ellps=GRS80 +units=m +no_defs

source

data-raw/gis/AMAPPS_10km_grid.tif

Source

https://www.fisheries.noaa.gov/new-england-mid-atlantic/population-assessments/atlantic-marine-assessment-program-protected
